cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on face recognition techniques and leveraging context for person recognition. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes a new framework that involves learning and reasoning, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions two large datasets, which indicates that it could belong to the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with issues of robustness and security, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
